/div>\n  </div>\n  <div class=\"col-md-4\">\n    <div style=\"background:#ffffff;border:1px solid #d0e4f0;border-radius:0.5rem;padding:1rem;box-shadow:0 1px 6px rgba(0,119,182,0.05);\">\n      <div style=\"color:#0a9e78;font-size:0.75rem;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-weight:700;margin-bottom:0.4rem;\">Formation</div>\n      <div style=\"font-weight:600;color:#023e8a;\">Osons l'Humanitaire — DIH</div>\n      <div style=\"font-size:0.85rem;color:#6a8aaa;\">Croix-Rouge de Belgique — 2026</div>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n  <div class=\"col-md-4\">\n    <div style=\"background:#ffffff;border:1px solid #d0e4f0;border-radius:0.5rem;padding:1rem;box-shadow:0 1px 6px rgba(0,119,182,0.05);\">\n      <div style=\"color:#0a9e78;font-size:0.75rem;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-weight:700;margin-bottom:0.4rem;\">Formation continue</div>\n      <div style=\"font-weight:600;color:#023e8a;\">MOOC FUN, MOOC ADF, Udemy</div>\n      <div style=\"font-size:0.85rem;color:#6a8aaa;\">R, Python, SIG, Machine Learning</div>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n</div>\n```\n\n\n---\n\n## 🌍 Langues\n\n| Langue   | Niveau     |\n|----------|------------|\n| Français | Courant    |\n| Anglais  | Débutant   |\n| Dioula   | Moyen      |\n| Grounssi | Moyen      |\n",
